This paper deals with logic and knowledge representation, which are central topics in computer science. The paper also discusses topological reasoning, which is relevant to several subfields of computer science such as artificial intelligence, data mining, and computational complexity. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.MS (Mathematical Software).
